; Test compare_by_commodity with prices in different currencies
; Covers commodity.cc lines 430-431 (recursion found disparity in price
; comparison with different commodity)

2024/01/01 Buy AAPL in USD
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash        $-1500.00

2024/01/02 Buy AAPL in EUR
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {130.00 EUR}
    Assets:EUR         -650.00 EUR

test bal --no-total --lots Brokerage
   10 AAPL {$150.00}
 5 AAPL {130.00 EUR}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
